  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to evaluate predictors of response to antipsychotic medication
      in subjects with schizophrenia. The investigators will evaluate psychopathology,brain MRI,
      genetics and neuropsychological profile. Two groups of treatment will be compared: first
      generation antipsychotics vs. second generation antipsychotics. Participants will be
      randomized to one of the groups. Trial duration: 12 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
