  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Schizophrenia or schizoaffective disorder

          -  Age: 18-45 years olde

          -  Less than 10 years of diagnosis

          -  Acute exacerbation of psychotic symptoms

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Use of clozapine

          -  Clinical unstable disease

          -  Delirium and cognitive disorders
      </textblock>
